{
  "video_id": "PYjWLqE_cfE",
  "title": "Why we need to imagine different futures | Anab Jain",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12968.0,
      "end_time": 15611.0,
      "text": "I visit the future for a living."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16265.0,
      "end_time": 17891.0,
      "text": "Not just one future,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17915.0,
      "end_time": 20160.0,
      "text": "but many possible futures,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20185.0,
      "end_time": 24304.0,
      "text": "bringing back evidences from those futures for you to experience today."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25197.0,
      "end_time": 27419.0,
      "text": "Like an archaeologist of the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28432.0,
      "end_time": 31163.0,
      "text": "Over the years, my many journeys have brought back things"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31188.0,
      "end_time": 34213.0,
      "text": "like a new species of synthetically engineered bees;"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 37520.0,
      "end_time": 39435.0,
      "text": "a book named, \"Pets as Protein;\""
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 40263.0,
      "end_time": 43427.0,
      "text": "a machine that makes you rich by trading your genetic data;"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 43451.0,
      "end_time": 45498.0,
      "text": "a lamp powered by sugar;"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 46450.0,
      "end_time": 47926.0,
      "text": "a computer for growing food."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 48573.0,
      "end_time": 52964.0,
      "text": "OK, so I don&#39;t actually travel to different futures -- yet."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 52988.0,
      "end_time": 55927.0,
      "text": "But my husband Jon and I spend a lot of time thinking"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 55951.0,
      "end_time": 59641.0,
      "text": "and creating visions of different futures in our studio."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 60810.0,
      "end_time": 62857.0,
      "text": "We are constantly looking out for weak signals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 62881.0,
      "end_time": 65254.0,
      "text": "those murmurs of future potential."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 65279.0,
      "end_time": 69352.0,
      "text": "Then we trace those threads of potential out into the future, asking:"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 69963.0,
      "end_time": 72497.0,
      "text": "What might it feel like to live in this future?"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 73680.0,
      "end_time": 75902.0,
      "text": "What might we see, hear and even breathe?"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 77157.0,
      "end_time": 81606.0,
      "text": "Then we run experiments, build prototypes, make objects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 81630.0,
      "end_time": 83660.0,
      "text": "bringing aspects of these futures to life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 83684.0,
      "end_time": 85996.0,
      "text": "making them concrete and tangible"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 86200.0,
      "end_time": 90774.0,
      "text": "so you can really feel the impact of those future possibilities"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 90798.0,
      "end_time": 91965.0,
      "text": "here and now."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 92936.0,
      "end_time": 95737.0,
      "text": "But this work is not about predictions."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 95761.0,
      "end_time": 97768.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s about creating tools --"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 97792.0,
      "end_time": 101256.0,
      "text": "tools that can help connect our present and our future selves"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 101280.0,
      "end_time": 105685.0,
      "text": "so we become active participants in creating a future we want --"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 105709.0,
      "end_time": 107565.0,
      "text": "a future that works for all."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 108758.0,
      "end_time": 110573.0,
      "text": "So how do we go about doing this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 111143.0,
      "end_time": 114487.0,
      "text": "For a recent project called Drone Aviary,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 114511.0,
      "end_time": 116480.0,
      "text": "we were interested in exploring"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 116730.0,
      "end_time": 119390.0,
      "text": "what it would mean to live with drones in our cities."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 119640.0,
      "end_time": 121896.0,
      "text": "Drones that have the power to see things we can&#39;t,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 121921.0,
      "end_time": 123673.0,
      "text": "to go places we can&#39;t"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 123697.0,
      "end_time": 125896.0,
      "text": "and to do so with increasing autonomy."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 126734.0,
      "end_time": 128323.0,
      "text": "But to understand the technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 128348.00000000001,
      "end_time": 130217.00000000001,
      "text": "getting our hands dirty was crucial."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 130651.00000000001,
      "end_time": 133482.0,
      "text": "So we built several different drones in our studio."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 133506.0,
      "end_time": 136610.0,
      "text": "We gave them names, functions and then flew them --"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 137395.0,
      "end_time": 138908.0,
      "text": "but not without difficulty."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 139413.0,
      "end_time": 140802.0,
      "text": "Things came loose,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 140826.0,
      "end_time": 142446.0,
      "text": "GPS signals glitched"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 142470.0,
      "end_time": 143882.0,
      "text": "and drones crashed."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 144599.0,
      "end_time": 146741.0,
      "text": "But it was through such experimentation"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 146765.0,
      "end_time": 150940.0,
      "text": "that we could construct a very concrete and very experiential slice"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 150964.0,
      "end_time": 152587.0,
      "text": "of one possible future."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 153613.0,
      "end_time": 155688.0,
      "text": "So now, let&#39;s go to that future."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 156199.0,
      "end_time": 159569.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s imagine we are living in a city with drones like this one."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 160196.0,
      "end_time": 162123.0,
      "text": "We call it The Nightwatchman."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 162756.0,
      "end_time": 166645.0,
      "text": "It patrols the streets, often spotted in the evenings and at night."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 167239.0,
      "end_time": 170639.0,
      "text": "Initially, many of us were annoyed by its low, dull hum."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 171144.0,
      "end_time": 173912.0,
      "text": "But then, like everything else, we got used to it."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 174423.0,
      "end_time": 177157.0,
      "text": "Now, what if you could see the world through its eyes?"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 178615.0,
      "end_time": 182937.0,
      "text": "See how it constantly logs every resident of our neighborhood;"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 182961.0,
      "end_time": 186281.0,
      "text": "logging the kids who play football in the no-ballgame area"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 186305.0,
      "end_time": 188752.0,
      "text": "and marking them as statutory nuisances."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 188776.0,
      "end_time": 190213.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 190237.0,
      "end_time": 194207.0,
      "text": "And then see how it disperses this other group, who are teenagers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 194231.0,
      "end_time": 197345.0,
      "text": "with the threat of an autonomously issued injunction."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 198387.0,
      "end_time": 201520.0,
      "text": "And then there&#39;s this giant floating disc called Madison."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 202203.0,
      "end_time": 204423.0,
      "text": "Its glaring presence is so overpowering,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 204447.0,
      "end_time": 206600.0,
      "text": "I can&#39;t help but stare at it."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 207242.0,
      "end_time": 209243.0,
      "text": "But if feels like each time I look at it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 209267.0,
      "end_time": 211810.0,
      "text": "it knows a little more about me --"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 211914.0,
      "end_time": 215780.0,
      "text": "like it keeps flashing all these Brianair adverts at me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 215103.0,
      "end_time": 217447.0,
      "text": "as if it knows about the holiday I&#39;m planning."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 218479.0,
      "end_time": 222206.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not sure if I find this mildly entertaining"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 222230.0,
      "end_time": 224420.0,
      "text": "or just entirely invasive."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 225684.0,
      "end_time": 227800.0,
      "text": "Back to the present."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 227611.0,
      "end_time": 229834.0,
      "text": "In creating this future, we learned a lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 230352.0,
      "end_time": 232958.0,
      "text": "Not just about how these machines work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 232982.0,
      "end_time": 235841.0,
      "text": "but what it would feel like to live alongside them."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 236239.0,
      "end_time": 238493.0,
      "text": "Whilst drones like Madison and Nightwatchman,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 238517.0,
      "end_time": 240340.0,
      "text": "in these particular forms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 240580.0,
      "end_time": 241599.0,
      "text": "are not real yet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 241623.0,
      "end_time": 245579.0,
      "text": "most elements of a drone future are in fact very real today."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 246264.0,
      "end_time": 247415.0,
      "text": "For instance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 247439.0,
      "end_time": 249753.0,
      "text": "facial recognition systems are everywhere --"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 249777.0,
      "end_time": 252186.0,
      "text": "in our phones, even in our thermostats"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 252211.0,
      "end_time": 254410.0,
      "text": "and in cameras around our cities --"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 254714.0,
      "end_time": 257459.0,
      "text": "keeping a record of everything we do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 257483.0,
      "end_time": 261668.0,
      "text": "whether it&#39;s an advertisement we glanced at or a protest we attended."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 261692.0,
      "end_time": 263363.0,
      "text": "These things are here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 263387.0,
      "end_time": 266111.0,
      "text": "and we often don&#39;t understand how they work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 266135.0,
      "end_time": 267985.0,
      "text": "and what their consequences could be."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 269279.0,
      "end_time": 270859.0,
      "text": "And we see this all around us."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 270883.0,
      "end_time": 272655.0,
      "text": "This difficulty in even imagining"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 272679.0,
      "end_time": 276823.0,
      "text": "how the consequences of our actions today will affect our future."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 277649.0,
      "end_time": 280534.0,
      "text": "Last year, where I live, in the UK, there was a referendum"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 280558.0,
      "end_time": 283820.0,
      "text": "where the people could vote for the UK to leave the EU"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 283107.0,
      "end_time": 284265.0,
      "text": "or stay in the EU,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 284289.0,
      "end_time": 285991.0,
      "text": "popularly known as \"Brexit.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 286819.0,
      "end_time": 288621.0,
      "text": "And soon after the results came out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 288645.0,
      "end_time": 291659.0,
      "text": "a word began to surface called \"Bregret\" --"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 291684.0,
      "end_time": 292724.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 292748.0,
      "end_time": 296183.0,
      "text": "describing people who chose to vote for Brexit as a protest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 296207.0,
      "end_time": 299296.0,
      "text": "but without thinking through its potential consequences."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 301127.0,
      "end_time": 304551.0,
      "text": "And this disconnect is evident in some of the simplest things."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 305795.0,
      "end_time": 307664.0,
      "text": "Say you go out for a quick drink."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 307688.0,
      "end_time": 310421.0,
      "text": "Then you decide you wouldn&#39;t mind a few more."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 310446.0,
      "end_time": 313660.0,
      "text": "You know you&#39;ll wake up in the morning feeling awful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 313900.0,
      "end_time": 314472.0,
      "text": "but you justify it by saying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 314496.0,
      "end_time": 316998.0,
      "text": "\"The other me in the future will deal with that.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 317607.0,
      "end_time": 319475.0,
      "text": "But as we find out in the morning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 319499.0,
      "end_time": 321464.0,
      "text": "that future \"you\" is you."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 322454.0,
      "end_time": 325651.0,
      "text": "When I was growing up in India in the late &#39;70s and early &#39;80s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 325675.0,
      "end_time": 326826.0,
      "text": "there was a feeling"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 326850.0,
      "end_time": 329837.0,
      "text": "that the future both needed to and could actually be planned."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 330343.0,
      "end_time": 333603.0,
      "text": "I remember my parents had to plan for some of the simplest things."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 333627.0,
      "end_time": 335656.0,
      "text": "When they wanted a telephone in our house,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 335680.0,
      "end_time": 337990.0,
      "text": "they needed to order it and then wait --"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 338140.0,
      "end_time": 341261.0,
      "text": "wait for nearly five years before it got installed in our house."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 341285.0,
      "end_time": 342319.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 342343.0,
      "end_time": 345841.0,
      "text": "And then if they wanted to call my grandparents who lived in another city,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 345865.0,
      "end_time": 348393.0,
      "text": "they needed to book something called a \"trunk call,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 348417.0,
      "end_time": 350676.0,
      "text": "and then wait again, for hours or even days."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 351298.0,
      "end_time": 354235.0,
      "text": "And then abruptly, the phone would ring at two in the morning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 354259.0,
      "end_time": 357509.0,
      "text": "and all of us would jump out of our beds and gather round the phone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 357533.0,
      "end_time": 359848.0,
      "text": "shrieking into it, discussing general well-being"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 359872.0,
      "end_time": 361205.0,
      "text": "at two in the morning."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 361229.0,
      "end_time": 365800.0,
      "text": "Today it can feel like things are happening too fast --"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 365330.0,
      "end_time": 367288.0,
      "text": "so fast, that it can become really difficult"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 367312.0,
      "end_time": 370269.0,
      "text": "for us to form an understanding of our place in history."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 370293.0,
      "end_time": 373720.0,
      "text": "It creates an overwhelming sense of uncertainty and anxiety,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 373744.0,
      "end_time": 376786.0,
      "text": "and so, we let the future just happen to us."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 378320.0,
      "end_time": 380270.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t connect with that future \"us.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 380528.0,
      "end_time": 382840.0,
      "text": "We treat our future selves as a stranger,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 382864.0,
      "end_time": 384832.0,
      "text": "and the future as a foreign land."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 385735.0,
      "end_time": 386920.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not a foreign land;"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 386944.0,
      "end_time": 388692.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s unfolding right in front of us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 388716.0,
      "end_time": 391280.0,
      "text": "continually being shaped by our actions today."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 391734.0,
      "end_time": 393224.0,
      "text": "We are that future,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 393940.0,
      "end_time": 396770.0,
      "text": "and so I believe fighting for a future we want"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 396794.0,
      "end_time": 399417.0,
      "text": "is more urgent and necessary than ever before."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 400297.0,
      "end_time": 401762.0,
      "text": "We have learned in our work"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 401786.0,
      "end_time": 405230.0,
      "text": "that one of the most powerful means of effecting change"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 405254.0,
      "end_time": 409398.0,
      "text": "is when people can directly, tangibly and emotionally experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 409422.0,
      "end_time": 412450.0,
      "text": "some of the future consequences of their actions today."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 413130.0,
      "end_time": 417104.0,
      "text": "Earlier this year, the government of the United Arab Emirates invited us"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 417128.0,
      "end_time": 419574.0,
      "text": "to help them shape their country&#39;s energy strategy"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 419598.0,
      "end_time": 421182.0,
      "text": "all the way up to 2050."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 421558.0,
      "end_time": 425816.0,
      "text": "Based on the government&#39;s econometric data, we created this large city model,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 425840.0,
      "end_time": 428907.0,
      "text": "and visualized many possible futures on it."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 430387.0,
      "end_time": 433707.0,
      "text": "As I was excitably taking a group of government officials"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 433731.0,
      "end_time": 435268.0,
      "text": "and members of energy companies"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 435292.0,
      "end_time": 437823.0,
      "text": "through one sustainable future on our model,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 437847.0,
      "end_time": 439577.0,
      "text": "one of the participants told me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 440122.0,
      "end_time": 443229.0,
      "text": "\"I cannot imagine that in the future people will stop driving cars"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 443253.0,
      "end_time": 445510.0,
      "text": "and start using public transport.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 445916.0,
      "end_time": 447760.0,
      "text": "And then he said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 447100.0,
      "end_time": 450706.0,
      "text": "\"There&#39;s no way I can tell my own son to stop driving his car.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 451927.0,
      "end_time": 453908.0,
      "text": "But we were prepared for this reaction."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 455208.0,
      "end_time": 458545.0,
      "text": "Working with scientists in a chemistry lab in my home city in India,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 458569.0,
      "end_time": 460744.0,
      "text": "we had created approximate samples"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 460768.0,
      "end_time": 465518.0,
      "text": "of what the air would be like in 2030 if our behavior stays the same."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 466493.0,
      "end_time": 469885.0,
      "text": "And so, I walked the group over to this object"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 469910.0,
      "end_time": 472257.0,
      "text": "that emits vapor from those air samples."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 473494.0,
      "end_time": 477500.0,
      "text": "Just one whiff of the noxious polluted air from 2030"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 477740.0,
      "end_time": 480191.0,
      "text": "brought home the point that no amount of data can."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 481690.0,
      "end_time": 484121.0,
      "text": "This is not the future you would want your children to inherit."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 484620.0,
      "end_time": 487185.0,
      "text": "The next day, the government made a big announcement."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 487209.0,
      "end_time": 490372.0,
      "text": "They would be investing billions of dollars in renewables."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 490396.0,
      "end_time": 494775.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t know what part our future experiences played in this decision,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 494799.0,
      "end_time": 497291.0,
      "text": "but we know that they&#39;ve changed their energy policy"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 497315.0,
      "end_time": 498799.0,
      "text": "to mitigate such a scenario."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 498823.0,
      "end_time": 502328.0,
      "text": "While something like air from the future is very effective and tangible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 502352.0,
      "end_time": 505181.0,
      "text": "the trajectory from our present to a future consequence"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 505206.0,
      "end_time": 506511.0,
      "text": "is not always so linear."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 507347.0,
      "end_time": 510520.0,
      "text": "Even when a technology is developed with utopian ideals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 510544.0,
      "end_time": 513276.0,
      "text": "the moment it leaves the laboratory and enters the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 513301.00000000006,
      "end_time": 516646.00000000006,
      "text": "it is subject to forces outside of the creators&#39; control."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 517616.0,
      "end_time": 521851.0,
      "text": "For one particular project, we investigated medical genomics:"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 521875.0,
      "end_time": 524966.0,
      "text": "the technology of gathering and using people&#39;s genetic data"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 524990.0,
      "end_time": 526849.0,
      "text": "to create personalized medicine."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 527268.0,
      "end_time": 528646.0,
      "text": "We were asking:"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 528670.0,
      "end_time": 532394.0,
      "text": "What are some of the unintended consequences of linking our genetics"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 532418.0,
      "end_time": 533579.0,
      "text": "to health care?"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 535175.0,
      "end_time": 537440.0,
      "text": "To explore this question further,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 537465.0,
      "end_time": 539357.0,
      "text": "we created a fictional lawsuit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 539914.0,
      "end_time": 544300.0,
      "text": "and brought it to life through 31 pieces of carefully crafted evidence."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 544783.0,
      "end_time": 547871.0,
      "text": "So we built an illegal genetic clinic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 547895.0,
      "end_time": 551780.0,
      "text": "a DIY carbon dioxide incubator,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 551102.0,
      "end_time": 553438.0,
      "text": "and even bought frozen mice on eBay."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 554273.0,
      "end_time": 557428.0,
      "text": "So now let&#39;s go to that future where this lawsuit is unfolding,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 557452.0,
      "end_time": 559574.0,
      "text": "and meet the defendant, Arnold Mann."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 560194.0,
      "end_time": 563759.0,
      "text": "Arnold is being prosecuted by this global giant biotech company"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 563783.0,
      "end_time": 565810.0,
      "text": "called Dynamic Genetics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 565627.0,
      "end_time": 567117.0,
      "text": "because they have evidence"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 567141.0,
      "end_time": 571731.0,
      "text": "that Arnold has illegally inserted the company&#39;s patented genetic material"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 571755.0,
      "end_time": 573249.0,
      "text": "into his body."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 573273.0,
      "end_time": 575863.0,
      "text": "How on earth did Arnold manage to do that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 576853.0,
      "end_time": 578260.0,
      "text": "Well, it all started"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 578510.0,
      "end_time": 582234.0,
      "text": "when Arnold was asked to submit a saliva sample in this spit kit"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 582258.0,
      "end_time": 583816.0,
      "text": "to the NHI --"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 583840.0,
      "end_time": 586790.0,
      "text": "the UK&#39;s National Health Insurance service."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 587289.0,
      "end_time": 590209.0,
      "text": "When Arnold received his health insurance bill,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 590233.0,
      "end_time": 591944.0,
      "text": "he was shocked and scared"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 591969.0,
      "end_time": 594351.0,
      "text": "to see that his premiums had gone through the roof,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 594375.0,
      "end_time": 597349.0,
      "text": "beyond anything he or his family could ever afford."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 597970.0,
      "end_time": 600651.0,
      "text": "The state&#39;s algorithm had scanned his genetic data"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 600675.0,
      "end_time": 604683.0,
      "text": "and found the risk of a chronic health condition lurking in his DNA."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 605135.0,
      "end_time": 608499.0,
      "text": "And so Arnold had to start paying toward the potential costs"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 608523.0,
      "end_time": 610199.0,
      "text": "of that future disease --"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 610223.0,
      "end_time": 612406.0,
      "text": "potential future disease from today."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 612430.0,
      "end_time": 614410.0,
      "text": "In that moment of fear and panic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 614660.0,
      "end_time": 615572.0,
      "text": "Arnold slipped through the city"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 615596.0,
      "end_time": 618654.0,
      "text": "into the dark shadows of this illegal clinic for treatment --"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 619457.0,
      "end_time": 621617.0,
      "text": "a treatment that would modify his DNA"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 621642.0,
      "end_time": 625300.0,
      "text": "so that the state&#39;s algorithm would no longer see him as a risk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 625324.0,
      "end_time": 628300.0,
      "text": "and his insurance premiums would become affordable again."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 628325.0,
      "end_time": 630100.0,
      "text": "But Arnold was caught."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 630340.0,
      "end_time": 634112.0,
      "text": "And the legal proceedings in the case Dynamic Genetics v. Mann began."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 634961.0,
      "end_time": 636653.0,
      "text": "In bringing such a future to life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 636677.0,
      "end_time": 639631.0,
      "text": "what was important to us was that people could actually touch,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 639655.0,
      "end_time": 641223.0,
      "text": "see and feel its potential,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 641757.0,
      "end_time": 644752.0,
      "text": "because such an immediate and close encounter provokes people"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 644776.0,
      "end_time": 646266.0,
      "text": "to ask the right questions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 646816.0,
      "end_time": 648870.0,
      "text": "questions like:"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 648111.0,
      "end_time": 650297.0,
      "text": "What are the implications of living in a world"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 650321.0,
      "end_time": 652310.0,
      "text": "where I&#39;m judged on my genetics?"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 653450.0,
      "end_time": 656185.0,
      "text": "Or: Who might claim ownership to my genetic data,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 656210.0,
      "end_time": 657720.0,
      "text": "and what might they do with it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 658918.0,
      "end_time": 662270.0,
      "text": "If this feels even slightly out-there or farfetched,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 662510.0,
      "end_time": 665843.0,
      "text": "today there&#39;s a little-known bill being passed through the American congress"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 665867.0,
      "end_time": 669915.0,
      "text": "known as HR 1313, Preserving Employee Wellness Programs Act."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 670455.0,
      "end_time": 674935.0,
      "text": "This bill proposes to amend the Genetic Information Nondiscrimination Act,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 674959.0,
      "end_time": 676665.0,
      "text": "popularly known as GINA,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 676689.0,
      "end_time": 679997.0,
      "text": "and would allow employers to ask about family medical history"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 680210.0,
      "end_time": 681204.0,
      "text": "and genetic data"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 681229.0,
      "end_time": 683798.0,
      "text": "to all employees for the first time."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 684938.0,
      "end_time": 687532.0,
      "text": "Those who refuse would face large penalties."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 689346.0,
      "end_time": 691100.0,
      "text": "In the work I&#39;ve shown so far,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 691124.0,
      "end_time": 693287.0,
      "text": "whether it was drones or genetic crimes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 693311.0,
      "end_time": 695669.0,
      "text": "these stories describe troubling futures"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 695693.0,
      "end_time": 698444.0,
      "text": "with the intention of helping us avoid those futures."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 699400.0,
      "end_time": 700981.0,
      "text": "But what about what we can&#39;t avoid?"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 701577.0,
      "end_time": 703669.0,
      "text": "Today, especially with climate change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 703693.0,
      "end_time": 705763.0,
      "text": "it looks like we are heading for trouble."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 706151.0,
      "end_time": 709349.0,
      "text": "And so what we want to do now is to prepare for that future"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 709374.0,
      "end_time": 713631.0,
      "text": "by developing tools and attitudes that can help us find hope --"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 714322.0,
      "end_time": 716940.0,
      "text": "hope that can inspire action."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 716908.0,
      "end_time": 719596.0,
      "text": "Currently, we are running an experiment in our studio."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 719620.0,
      "end_time": 721970.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a work in progress."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 721539.0,
      "end_time": 723763.0,
      "text": "Based on climate data projections,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 723787.0,
      "end_time": 725343.0,
      "text": "we are exploring a future"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 725367.0,
      "end_time": 728800.0,
      "text": "where the Western world has moved from abundance to scarcity."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 728824.0,
      "end_time": 732234.0,
      "text": "We imagine living in a future city with repeated flooding,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 732259.0,
      "end_time": 734996.0,
      "text": "periods with almost no food in supermarkets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 735200.0,
      "end_time": 736756.0,
      "text": "economic instabilities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 736780.0,
      "end_time": 738464.0,
      "text": "broken supply chains."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 739111.0,
      "end_time": 743167.0,
      "text": "What can we do to not just survive, but prosper in such a world?"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 744150.0,
      "end_time": 745361.0,
      "text": "What food can we eat?"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 746163.0,
      "end_time": 747982.0,
      "text": "To really step inside these questions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 748600.0,
      "end_time": 751819.0,
      "text": "we are building this room in a flat in London from 2050."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 752654.0,
      "end_time": 755970.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s like a little time capsule that we reclaimed from the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 755994.0,
      "end_time": 758140.0,
      "text": "We stripped it down to the bare minimum."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 758164.0,
      "end_time": 760690.0,
      "text": "Everything we lovingly put in our homes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 760940.0,
      "end_time": 761770.0,
      "text": "like flat-panel TVs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 761794.0,
      "end_time": 763590.0,
      "text": "internet-connected fridges"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 763614.0,
      "end_time": 765430.0,
      "text": "and artisanal furnishings"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 765670.0,
      "end_time": 766389.0,
      "text": "all had to go."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 766413.0,
      "end_time": 769315.0,
      "text": "And in its place, we&#39;re building food computers"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 769339.0,
      "end_time": 772193.0,
      "text": "from abandoned, salvaged and repurposed materials,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 772715.0,
      "end_time": 775122.0,
      "text": "turning today&#39;s waste into tomorrow&#39;s dinner."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 776707.0,
      "end_time": 777858.0,
      "text": "For instance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 777882.0,
      "end_time": 781870.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve just finished building our first fully automated fogponics machine."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 781894.0,
      "end_time": 785310.0,
      "text": "It uses the technique of fogponics -- so just fog as a nutrient,"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 785334.0,
      "end_time": 786912.0,
      "text": "not even water or soil --"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 786937.0,
      "end_time": 788332.0,
      "text": "to grow things quickly."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 789324.0,
      "end_time": 790543.0,
      "text": "At the moment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 790567.0,
      "end_time": 792291.0,
      "text": "we have successfully grown tomatoes."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 793254.0,
      "end_time": 796381.0,
      "text": "But we&#39;ll need more food than what we can grow in this small room."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 796705.0,
      "end_time": 798940.0,
      "text": "So what else could we forage from the city?"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 799509.0,
      "end_time": 802881.0,
      "text": "Insects? Pigeons? Foxes?"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 805794.0,
      "end_time": 808363.0,
      "text": "Earlier, we brought back air from the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 808387.0,
      "end_time": 811109.0,
      "text": "This time we are bringing an entire room from the future,"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 811134.0,
      "end_time": 813481.0,
      "text": "a room full of hope, tools and tactics"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 813505.0,
      "end_time": 816640.0,
      "text": "to create positive action in hostile conditions."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 817384.0,
      "end_time": 818975.0,
      "text": "Spending time in this room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 818999.0,
      "end_time": 821620.0,
      "text": "a room that could be our own future home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 821860.0,
      "end_time": 824648.0,
      "text": "makes the consequences of climate change and food insecurity"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 824672.0,
      "end_time": 826911.0,
      "text": "much more immediate and tangible."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 829550.0,
      "end_time": 832830.0,
      "text": "What we&#39;re learning through such experiments and our practice"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 832107.0,
      "end_time": 833598.0,
      "text": "and the people we engage with"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 833622.0,
      "end_time": 835872.0,
      "text": "is that creating concrete experiences"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 835897.0,
      "end_time": 839210.0,
      "text": "can bridge the disconnect between today and tomorrow."
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 839761.0,
      "end_time": 842655.0,
      "text": "By putting ourselves into different possible futures,"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 842679.0,
      "end_time": 844241.0,
      "text": "by becoming open and willing"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 844265.0,
      "end_time": 848605.0,
      "text": "to embrace the uncertainty and discomfort that such an act can bring,"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 848629.0,
      "end_time": 851714.0,
      "text": "we have the opportunity to imagine new possibilities."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 852223.0,
      "end_time": 854127.0,
      "text": "We can find optimistic futures;"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 854151.0,
      "end_time": 855992.0,
      "text": "we can find paths forward;"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 856160.0,
      "end_time": 858680.0,
      "text": "we can move beyond hope into action."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 858781.0,
      "end_time": 862600.0,
      "text": "It means we have the chance to change direction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 862966.0,
      "end_time": 865119.0,
      "text": "a chance to have our voices heard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 865832.0,
      "end_time": 870470.0,
      "text": "a chance to write ourselves into a future we want."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 871548.0,
      "end_time": 873586.0,
      "text": "Other worlds are possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 874469.0,
      "end_time": 875636.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 875660.0,
      "end_time": 878848.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}